pirit, A Guide </div><div class="t m115a x86 h49 y29f5 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 14:26) </div><div class="t m814 x5a h49 y2a3b ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m4f x86 h49 y2a2a ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Accepting the Spirit&apos;s Guidance </div><div class="t m14db x86 h49 y2a0e ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Rom. 8:4) </div><div class="t m66d x5a h49 y2284 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t mee x86 h49 y28d8 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Spirit Guides Through the </div><div class="t maaa x86 h49 y2120 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Word </div><div class="t m1199 x86 h49 y20e9 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Eph. 6:17) </div><div class="t m7e1 x5a h49 y4f8 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><div class="t m1347 x86 h49 y4f8 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Guide Amid Persecution </div><div class="t m906 x86 h49 y13ab ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(2 Tim. 3:12; Rev. 12:17) </div><div class="t m2ef x5a h49 y1164 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">5. </div><div class="t m1519 x86 h49 y1165 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">An Example of the Spirit&apos;s Guidance </div><div class="t m115f x86 h49 y2032 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Luke 2:2530) </div><div class="t mb27 x5a h49 y1081 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">6. </div><div class="t m67c x86 h49 y11db ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Spirit Guides to Jesus </div><div class="t m1494 x86 h49 y15df ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 16:14) </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
